pr_body:
This PR provides:

1. The boundary oracles for lines intersecting a spectrahedron that can be used by the existing random walks.
2. Reflection oracles that can be used by the billiard walk class.

The generalized eigenvalue problems are solved by Spectra.

The implementation can be used by the existing volume algorithms when an interior point is given as input.
